OL,3,CThirteen winters of damp: Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents suffer after botched
OL,5,Cinsulation scheme
OL,7,FIn the Llynfi Valley, cold winters are
OL,8,Fnothing new.
OL,10,FBut in Caerau, it cuts deeper than it
OL,11,Fshould.
OL,13,FFamilies here are preparing for their
OL,14,F13th living with damp, mould and the
OL,15,Ffallout of a government-funded
OL,16,Finsulation scheme gone wrong.
OL,18,FStreet by street, pockmarked homes
OL,19,Fshow where external cladding and glued-
OL,20,Fon insulation have been stripped away,
OL,21,Fmarking a long, messy trail of repairs.
