OL,7,FThe repair work is in its final
OL,8,Fstages, but many residents are
OL,9,Funderstandably sceptical and unhappy
OL,10,Fwith what they've seen so far.
OL,12,FThree years ago, ITV News met Julie
OL,13,FGoodridge, who showed us the damp room
OL,14,Fshe'd slept in for nearly a decade.
OL,16,FJulie suffered from respiratory
OL,17,Fproblems, and told us she "couldn't
OL,18,Fcope".
