OL,7,FJulie died last year. Her son Geraint
OL,8,Fsaid he's "heartbroken" that she never
OL,9,Fsaw the home she used to love put
OL,10,Fright.
OL,12,FWe also revisited Rhiannon, who first
OL,13,Fspoke to ITV News in 2022. She told us
OL,14,Fher electric sockets would regularly
OL,15,Fcut out due to her extremely damp
OL,16,Fwalls.
OL,18,FThree years later, little has changed
OL,19,Finside her home.
