OL,7,FShe lives with a teenage daughter and
OL,8,Fa husband battling incurable cancer.
OL,9,FHer property is still marked by damp
OL,10,Fand black mould.
OL,12,FThe problems stretch back more than a
OL,13,Fdecade.
OL,15,FIn 2012, the insulation contracts for
OL,16,Fa Welsh government scheme called Arbed
OL,17,Fwere awarded to a company run by a
OL,18,FLabour cabinet member of Bridgend
OL,19,FCouncil who has since died.
