OL,7,FA later internal audit by the council
OL,8,Ffound major failings in the project,
OL,9,Fwith no formal procurement process
OL,10,Ffollowed and no due diligence checks
OL,11,Fcarried out.
OL,13,FLast month, a National Audit Office
OL,14,Freport found that tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fhomes across the UK, fitted with
OL,16,Fsimilar external insulation under
OL,17,Fgovernment schemes, now require
OL,18,Frepairs.
