OL,7,FCaerau is far from alone, but
OL,8,Fresidents here say they've been living
OL,9,Fwith the consequences longer than most.
OL,11,FBridgend Council said the Caerau
OL,12,Frepair programme is now in its "final
OL,13,Fstages", with completion expected next
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FIt said 63 properties are registered
OL,17,Ffor remedial works, including dozens
OL,18,Ffor which the council says it is not
OL,19,Fresponsible.
