OL,7,FA spokesperson told ITV News: "In
OL,8,Fpartnership with our contractor,
OL,9,FWarmworks, significant progress has
OL,10,Fbeen made with the Caerau wall
OL,11,Finsulation remedial works and all
OL,12,Fregistered eligible properties have
OL,13,Fnow had the previous insulation
OL,14,Fremoved and new ventilation installed.
