OL,7,F"Aided by new ventilation, each
OL,8,Fproperty is undergoing a drying-out
OL,9,Fperiod. Once moisture readings reach
OL,10,Fappropriate levels, new cement render
OL,11,For external wall insulation will be
OL,12,Finstalled in line with nationally
OL,13,Faccredited standards."
OL,15,FBut after more than a decade of
OL,16,Fdelays, many residents remain
OL,17,Fsceptical. Some want more than
OL,18,Frepairs; they want compensation.
OL,20,FFor now, only one of those looks
OL,21,Fwithin reach.
